        <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem;">
            <p>
                <strong>Source-License API v2.0.0</strong> -
                <a href="https://github.com/PixelRidgeSoftworks/Source-License" target="_blank">GitHub Repository</a> |
